The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to detect image splicing attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper deals with image forensics, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
